rows.label: tlk43500147_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Head down this way and you'll
reach a shop called Malbren
Salvaging. Heard of it?

rows.label: tlk43500147_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Yeah, salvaging's not the most active
of businesses round here.

rows.label: tlk43500147_03_msg0003
rows.name: It's as silent as the grave around there.

rows.label: tlk43500147_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I feel bad for them. You should really
go pay them a visit.

rows.label: tlk43500147_03_msg0005
rows.name:
They've probably got a different
selection by now.
